        "blog.posts.como-escribir-guiones-virales-tiktok-2025.title": "How to Write Viral TikTok Scripts in 2025",
        "blog.posts.como-escribir-guiones-virales-tiktok-2025.excerpt": "Discover proven techniques to create TikTok scripts that generate millions of views. Includes real examples and free templates.",
